creator: Android Buddy
descriptionHtml:
This App is very useful to you if you require to forward your calls to other numbers. Instead of going to settings and taking headache of accessing call forwarding system, use our application and In one click you all call will be forwarded to target number.

You just need to put the required number in the text-box and on click of 'Forward' button, your call will be redirected to that number and you can see the notification also of call forwarding active.

Key Features:
Call Forwarding App,
Call to Another Call,
Divert Call,
One to one call,
All condition call
All busy call
descriptionShort: Call Forwarding is easy and simple application to use.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Under the hood changes to deliver the better performance
